title: Three by Three Jotblock Chunky Sketchpad
description:
In classic jOTBLOCK form, these super thick sketchpads boast incorporated holes to store color pencils (included with each), inviting full creative expression at the moment of inspiration.

Chunky pad includes 6 pencils / 550 sheets

Size:  Length: 4.75 in L x 4.25 W x 3.25 H
